knowledgeGraph.title: Mercy San Juan Medical Center
knowledgeGraph.description: Mercy San Juan Medical Center is a not-for-profit hospital located in Carmichael, California serving the areas of north Sacramento County and south Placer County. It is home to Sacramento's first Comprehensive Stroke Center.

organic.title: Mercy San Juan Medical Center - Sacramento - Dignity Health
organic.snippet: Dignity Health Mercy San Juan Medical Center has been serving Carmichael for over 45 years and has the only stroke center north of the bay area.
